{"article_id":"9ztOSlP3bWcuIqGR","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"More than 300 news outlets have launched a campaign","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"to counter US President Donald Trump 's attacks","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"and promote a free press .","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"The Boston Globe made the call last week for a nationwide denouncement of the president 's `` dirty war '' against the media ,","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"using the hashtag # EnemyOfNone .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"Mr Trump has derided media reports as `` fake news ''","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"and attacked journalists as `` enemies of the people '' .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"And he tweeted on Thursday :","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"`` The fake news media is the opposition party . ''","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"`` It is very bad for our great country ...","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"But we are winning ! ''","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"UN experts have warned","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"that Mr Trump 's comments about the media raise the risk of violence against journalists .","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"The Boston Globe had pledged to write an editorial `` on the dangers of the administration 's assault on the press '' on 16 August ,","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"and asked others to do the same .","depth":5},{"id":15,"text":"The initial positive response from 100 news organisations has grown closer to 350","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"with major US national newspapers and smaller local outlets answering the call ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"along with international publications like the UK newspaper The Guardian .","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"Starting with the Boston Globe itself ,","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"the editorial there ,","depth":12},{"id":20,"text":"headlined Journalists Are Not The Enemy ,","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"argued","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"that a free press had been a core American principle for more than 200 years itself ,","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"the editorial there ,","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"headlined Journalists Are Not The Enemy ,","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"argued","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"that a free press had been a core American principle for more than 200 years","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"The New York Times chose the headline","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"A Free Press Needs You ,","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"calling Mr Trump 's attacks `` dangerous to the lifeblood of democracy '' .","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"It published excerpts from dozens more publications beneath","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"chose the headline A Free Press Needs You ,","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"calling Mr Trump 's attacks `` dangerous to the lifeblood of democracy '' .","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"It published excerpts from dozens more publications beneath","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"The New York Post","depth":13},{"id":35,"text":"- a pro-Trump tabloid -","depth":13},{"id":36,"text":"answered the Globe 's call","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"by saying","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"`` Who are we to disagree ? ''","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"adding :","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"`` It may be frustrating to argue","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"that","depth":14},{"id":42,"text":"just because we print inconvenient truths","depth":15},{"id":43,"text":"does n't mean that we 're fake news ,","depth":15},{"id":44,"text":"but being a journalist is n't a popularity contest .","depth":13},{"id":45,"text":"All we can do","depth":14},{"id":46,"text":"is to keep reporting . ''","depth":14},{"id":47,"text":"But it also said :","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"`` Will this make a difference ?","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"Not one whit ''","depth":15},{"id":50,"text":"- a pro-Trump tabloid -","depth":15},{"id":51,"text":"answered the Globe 's call","depth":14},{"id":52,"text":"by saying","depth":14},{"id":53,"text":"`` Who are we to disagree ? ''","depth":14},{"id":54,"text":"adding :","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"`` It may be frustrating to argue","depth":15},{"id":56,"text":"that","depth":16},{"id":57,"text":"just because we print inconvenient truths","depth":18},{"id":58,"text":"does n't mean","depth":18},{"id":59,"text":"that we 're fake news ,","depth":17},{"id":60,"text":"but being a journalist is n't a popularity contest .","depth":15},{"id":61,"text":"All","depth":17},{"id":62,"text":"we can do","depth":17},{"id":63,"text":"is to keep reporting . ''","depth":16},{"id":64,"text":"But it also said :","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"`` Will this make a difference ?","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"Not one whit ''","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"The Topeka Capital-Journal was another paper","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"to join the campaign .","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"It said of Mr Trump 's attack on the media :","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"`` It 's sinister .","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"It 's destructive .","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"And it must end now . ''","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"The paper was one of the few","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"to endorse Mr Trump in 2016 .","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"The fact","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"that Mr Trump won","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"without such media endorsements","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"may cast doubt on whether the Globe 's campaign would actually dent his support .","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"Later on Thursday , President Trump tweeted","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"that the Globe `` is in collusion with other papers on free press '' .","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"There have been some dissenting voices to the Globe 's campaign :","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"At the conservative website Townhall.com , Tom Tradup panned the Globe 's `` pathetic bid","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"to pretend","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"it is still relevant '' ,","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"writing :","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"`` I would not presume to tell anyone else what to think or what to do .","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"But as for me","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"- and I suspect many others -","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"I wo n't be putting any coins in any newspaper box August 16th . ''","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"The Wall Street Journal declined to take part .","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"An earlier piece by James Freeman argued","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"Mr Trump was entitled to free speech ,","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"and the Globe 's drive ran counter to the very independence","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"it was seeking .","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"Trust in the media has dipped to an all-time low ,","depth":5},{"id":96,"text":"and Mr Trump has tapped into this well of discontent ,","depth":6},{"id":97,"text":"prompting journalistic outcry .","depth":6},{"id":98,"text":"In fact `` the media ''","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"- in popular parlance -","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"means an amorphous blob of TV networks .","depth":6},{"id":101,"text":"Even people in flyover country , a region","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"where voters supported Mr Trump ,","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"see individual reporters in a more nuanced way ,","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"as I 've discovered .","depth":7},{"id":105,"text":"Recently I was interviewing someone in a Kansas liquor store","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"( it 's a long story )","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"and a big , burly construction worker burst in the door","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"and shouted :","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"`` The media ! ''","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"I looked up uneasily ,","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"and he smiled","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"and said","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"I was doing important work .","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"When Mr Trump attacks `` the media '' ,","depth":6},{"id":115,"text":"crowds roar .","depth":6},{"id":116,"text":"In general terms , people condemn `` the media '' .","depth":7},{"id":117,"text":"Privately , though , Mr Trump is chummy with us","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"-","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"and often asks","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"how we 're doing .","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"And ordinary people across the US are also gracious towards journalists ,","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"showing a real appreciation for their work .","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"A poll","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"released on Tuesday by Quinnipiac University","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"suggested","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"that 51 % of Republican voters now believed the media to be `` the enemy of the people rather than an important part of democracy ''","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"and 52 % of the Republican supporters","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"polled","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"were not concerned","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"that Mr Trump 's criticism would lead to violence against journalists .","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"Among all voters , 65 % believe the news media to be an important part of democracy ,","depth":8},{"id":132,"text":"the poll suggests .","depth":8},{"id":133,"text":"An Ipsos poll , also this month , gave similar figures .","depth":5},{"id":134,"text":"In addition it found","depth":6},{"id":135,"text":"that 23 % of Republicans , and about one in eight Americans overall , believed","depth":7},{"id":136,"text":"Mr Trump should close down mainstream news outlets like CNN , the Washington Post and the New York Times .","depth":7},{"id":137,"text":"Mr Trump has certainly ramped up the pressure on mainstream media with numerous tweets .","depth":3},{"id":138,"text":"The Trump Twitter Archive says","depth":4},{"id":139,"text":"he has tweeted 281 times so far","depth":5},{"id":140,"text":"using the term `` fake news '' .","depth":5},{"id":141,"text":"When he brings up the matter at his rallies ,","depth":4},{"id":142,"text":"some journalists have felt uneasy about their safety","depth":5},{"id":143,"text":"and have even avoided using designated reporter zones .","depth":5},{"id":144,"text":"At a presidential rally in Florida in July , CNN filmed Mr Trump 's supporters","depth":9},{"id":145,"text":"yelling insults and swearing at reporters","depth":10},{"id":146,"text":"covering the event .","depth":10},{"id":147,"text":"CNN presenter Jim Acosta tweeted a clip ,","depth":9},{"id":148,"text":"which contained strong language .","depth":9},{"id":149,"text":"A man was also arrested in January","depth":8},{"id":150,"text":"for making threats to CNN employees via telephone calls","depth":9},{"id":151,"text":"that referred to `` fake news '' .","depth":9},{"id":152,"text":"The publisher of the New York Times , AG Sulzberger , told Mr Trump in a personal meeting in July","depth":7},{"id":153,"text":"that the president 's language was `` contributing to a rise in threats against journalists","depth":8},{"id":154,"text":"and will lead to violence '' .","depth":8},{"id":155,"text":"But most of the Globe 's campaign is about maintaining a free press","depth":6},{"id":156,"text":"and its own editorial does not even touch on violence .","depth":6},{"id":157,"text":"Some outlets do , however , refer to the recent killing of five people at the offices of the Capital Gazette in Maryland .","depth":5},{"id":158,"text":"This , and an incident","depth":9},{"id":159,"text":"in which two journalists were killed live on air in Virginia in 2015 ,","depth":10},{"id":160,"text":"well before Mr Trump was elected ,","depth":10},{"id":161,"text":"are used","depth":8},{"id":162,"text":"to highlight the dangers of the profession ,","depth":7},{"id":163,"text":"although both were allegedly carried out by people with personal grievances .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":327,"left":300,"right":326,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":300,"left":258,"right":299,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":258,"left":176,"right":257,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":176,"left":168,"right":175,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":168,"left":166,"right":167